# For Debain and all distributions based on it:

[Tools you will need]:

1.  sudo apt update

2. Git (A tool for downloading projects from GitHub):
    sudo apt install git

3. Curl (A tool for downloading files and projects from the internet):
    sudo apt install curl
    
4.  Fish (A command-line shell):
    sudo apt install fish
    
5.  Kitty (A terminal):
    sudo apt install kitty
    
6.  Starship (A cross-shell prompt):
    curl -sS https://starship.rs/install.sh | sh
